          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Relationships",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3797,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/12/237301566/5968bc73f375ee1e3704302541c83c7f_5877733374426459671.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Ли Юэ",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "3,700 years ago, Morax founded Liyue and contracted with the Adepti to protect the city. 37 centuries later, Rex Lapis faked his death to test whether the people of Liyue could live without his protection. When the mortals passed the test, Morax stepped down as Archon for the people and began to live the life of a mortal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5102,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/01/237301566/7372a2d1b47769b64d0e87bd21a867a7_6277812751920026426.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Адепты",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Morax is the Prime of Adepti. Together with other Adepti, he ruled Liyue.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3487,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/01/70239714/5e065c30389a33ac291a2adf4f59cf71_771678854028551873.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Гуй Чжун",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2552,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/20/237301566/f85da71c0716edf2cd8333f3b9c55a9c_5730904652047291178.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Гоба",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Morax's friends",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4784,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2023/12/20/472a219c5d998c371672b670a0829f16_7380212387492663867.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Аждаха",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Rex Lapis gave Azhdaha sight and made a contract with him to protect Liyue. When the erosion caused Azhdaha to forget his agreement and attack the people, Morax tried to share his power with him to stop the erosion, but was forced to seal his friend away.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4904,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/02/237301566/6dfc1c5f5f69b627eb5428b304e30377_6627017400427115689.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Осиал",
