                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Fatui Harbinger who tried to obtain the Geo Gnosis. He awakened Osial so that the Geo Archon, who had faked his death, would be forced to return and save Liyue.",
                      "type": "text"
